Build-Depends: librpc
Section: net
Category: Network
Title: Lightweight Network Intrusion Detection System (MySQL)
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: snort-2.9.2.2.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:     Snort is an open source network intrusion detection and prevention system.
  It is capable of performing real-time traffic analysis, alerting, blocking
  and packet logging on IP networks.  It utilizes a combination of protocol
  analysis and pattern matching in order to detect anomalies, misuse and
  attacks.
  This package contains snort with support for logging to a MySQL database.
http://www.snort.org/
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
